# Create box plot for outliner treatment
Q1 = df['mpg'].quantile(0.25)
Q3 = df['mpg'].quantile(0.75)
IQR = Q3-Q1
print(Q1)
print(Q3)
print(IQR)
lower = Q1 - (1.5 * IQR)
upper = Q3 + (1.5 * IQR)
print(lower, upper)
